1
00:01:55,455 --> 00:02:02,161
[giggles]

2
00:02:02,194 --> 00:02:04,296
{\an1}Forehead! Forehead!
Forehead!

3
00:02:04,330 --> 00:02:07,600
Hmf! Hey! Knock it
off! Leave me alone!

4
00:02:07,632 --> 00:02:11,570
[giggles]

5
00:02:11,604 --> 00:02:13,371
Okay!

6
00:02:14,706 --> 00:02:17,242
[gasp] ...It's
snowing...

7
00:02:17,275 --> 00:02:20,278
Kon, kon, kon,
it's snowing, kon!

8
00:02:20,311 --> 00:02:23,046
{\an1}It looks to me
like Yota really
likes you, Sakura.

9
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:25,015
Or your forehead
at least..!

10
00:02:25,048 --> 00:02:26,417
Perfect!

11
00:02:26,451 --> 00:02:29,686
Listen..! What's
the deal..!?

12
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:33,689
Kon, kon, kon!
Kon, kon, kon!

13
00:02:35,092 --> 00:02:38,362
Well... I guess
this could be fun!

14
00:03:08,356 --> 00:03:12,493
All I wanted to do was
give Sasuke a bouquet of
flowers from our shop...

15
00:03:12,526 --> 00:03:16,463
{\an1}...but he just ignored me
and walked off without so
much as a look!

16
00:03:16,497 --> 00:03:20,700
So so sad.
Poor Ino-Ino...

17
00:03:20,733 --> 00:03:23,203
{\an1}Ino... I... sorry.

18
00:03:23,236 --> 00:03:27,807
Yota..! You're so nice
that I'll give you one!

19
00:03:29,708 --> 00:03:34,813
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Ino is so forward...</i>
<i>I can't believe she'd</i>
<i>act that way with Sasuke!</i>

20
00:03:34,846 --> 00:03:37,450
You having
fun, Sakura?

21
00:03:37,483 --> 00:03:38,417
{\an1}Huh?

22
00:03:38,450 --> 00:03:40,653
{\an1}If Sakura happy,
then Yota happy, too!

23
00:03:40,687 --> 00:03:43,455
Sakura...!? What are
you so happy about!?

24
00:03:43,488 --> 00:03:45,257
{\an1}Oh...! That's
not it...!

25
00:03:45,290 --> 00:03:47,559
[giggle]

26
00:03:47,593 --> 00:03:49,126
[annoyed groan]

27
00:03:51,729 --> 00:03:54,098
That yota is
so fickle!

28
00:03:54,131 --> 00:03:58,202
{\an4}When he's sad, it
starts raining. And
when he's happy, it
snows... Hm...

29
00:03:58,236 --> 00:04:01,138
{\an1}[groaning]

30
00:04:01,172 --> 00:04:02,440
{\an1}Huh?

31
00:04:17,220 --> 00:04:18,488
Huh?

32
00:04:20,490 --> 00:04:21,890
{\an3}Huh?

33
00:04:21,924 --> 00:04:24,326
<i>(Ino)</i>
<i>Those flowers...</i>

34
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:25,728
<i>(Shikamaru)</i>
<i>Did Yota...?</i>

35
00:04:27,496 --> 00:04:28,896
He was here?

36
00:04:28,930 --> 00:04:29,732
{\an3}Huh...

37
00:04:31,333 --> 00:04:33,134
No, you can't go
there, Yota...

38
00:04:33,167 --> 00:04:35,704
You're supposed to
be a secret from the
rest of the village.

39
00:04:35,738 --> 00:04:39,207
If someone discovered
you, then there's gonna
be trouble for sure!

40
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:41,409
{\an1}So you can't let
anybody see you,
okay?

41
00:04:41,442 --> 00:04:44,178
Sure! But don't
worry, no one's
seen me.

42
00:04:44,212 --> 00:04:45,413
{\an1}Are you sure?

43
00:04:45,446 --> 00:04:48,650
You bet! Well,
maybe one kid...

44
00:04:48,683 --> 00:04:49,550
{\an1}Who!?

45
00:04:49,584 --> 00:04:51,551
{\an1}He seemed like kind
of a weird one...

46
00:04:51,585 --> 00:04:54,755
He was the only
kid sitting outside
at lunch.

47
00:04:54,787 --> 00:04:56,423
He was on
an iron rod.

48
00:04:56,456 --> 00:04:58,191
{\an1}Iron rod?

49
00:04:58,225 --> 00:04:59,825
{\an1}...Naruto?

50
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:10,770
Hm... Wait, you
mean... that kid?

51
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:21,813
{\an1}Oh! I know! He's
always alone! And
looks really angry.

52
00:05:21,846 --> 00:05:26,751
Angry? Really? 'Cause
every time I see him
he kinda smiles at me.

53
00:05:26,785 --> 00:05:29,286
{\an1}You know what,
maybe he likes you!

54
00:05:29,321 --> 00:05:31,355
What!? Cut it out!

55
00:05:31,388 --> 00:05:33,792
{\an1}Did Naruto notice
you, or not?

56
00:05:33,824 --> 00:05:37,328
{\an1}Maybe... I dunno.

57
00:05:37,361 --> 00:05:41,265
{\an1}Listen, Yota. Don't
go into the village
ever again, okay?

58
00:05:41,298 --> 00:05:45,234
{\an4}If you're caught, you
might get taken away
and we wouldn't see
each other again.

59
00:05:45,268 --> 00:05:49,439
Oh no, not that!
I don't want to be
apart from Sakura!

60
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,941
{\an1}Just Sakura?
What gives?

61
00:05:51,974 --> 00:05:53,609
Thank you, Yota.

62
00:05:53,643 --> 00:05:56,346
I gotta say, that
was really pretty
funny, though.

63
00:05:56,379 --> 00:06:01,483
{\an5}Sasuke is always
so "cool," but he
looked like a
flower garden!

64
00:06:01,516 --> 00:06:07,389
[laughter]

65
00:06:19,866 --> 00:06:21,968
[grunt]

66
00:06:29,677 --> 00:06:31,846
[panting]

67
00:06:35,382 --> 00:06:37,916
So, does this mean we
have to fight Yota?

68
00:06:39,786 --> 00:06:42,789
{\an1}It's just like with
Asuma. We have to
fight and seal him.

69
00:06:42,822 --> 00:06:45,224
{\an1}...We have to fight!

70
00:06:45,591 --> 00:06:47,726
Yeah, but...
How can we!?

71
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:50,729
{\an5}<i>(Choji)</i>
<i>How do we defeat</i>
<i>someone who can</i>
<i>control the weather?</i>

72
00:06:50,763 --> 00:06:52,431
{\an1}I don't know yet!

73
00:06:52,464 --> 00:06:53,665
[shouts]

74
00:06:54,065 --> 00:06:56,134
[panting]

75
00:06:56,167 --> 00:07:00,772
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>Come to think of it, we</i>
<i>really don't know much of</i>
<i>anything about Yota...</i>

76
00:07:01,906 --> 00:07:03,641
{\an8}<i>...How do we...?</i>

77
00:07:05,008 --> 00:07:07,445
{\an8}<i>(Telepathically)</i>
<i>Dad, connect me</i>
<i>with Sakura.</i>

78
00:07:07,478 --> 00:07:08,646
[gasp]

79
00:07:09,414 --> 00:07:10,681
You got it.

80
00:07:12,482 --> 00:07:13,751
Sakura!

81
00:07:13,785 --> 00:07:14,618
[gasp]

82
00:07:14,651 --> 00:07:16,520
{\an8}<i>(Ino)</i>
<i>Sakura! You there?</i>

83
00:07:16,553 --> 00:07:19,856
{\an8}<i>(Telepathically)</i>
<i>Ino? Sorry, I'm in the</i>
<i>middle of something</i>
<i>right now!</i>

84
00:07:19,890 --> 00:07:23,993
{\an7}<i>Do you remember...?</i>
<i>You have to-- You</i>
<i>just have to! </i>

85
00:07:24,026 --> 00:07:24,994
{\an8}<i>(Ino)</i>
<i>...It's Yota!</i>

86
00:07:26,797 --> 00:07:31,000
{\an7}<i>Wait... Yota? Ino...</i>
<i>He's in front of me</i>
<i>right now!</i>

87
00:07:31,033 --> 00:07:34,002
{\an1}[gasp] <i>What..!? He is!?</i>

88
00:07:34,035 --> 00:07:34,737
[gasp]

89
00:07:34,770 --> 00:07:36,037
{\an3}Huh!?

90
00:07:40,575 --> 00:07:42,377
{\an7}<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>He's here, too!</i>

91
00:07:42,410 --> 00:07:43,445
[gasp]

92
00:07:43,478 --> 00:07:45,447
{\an7}<i>...And he's really</i>
<i>really mad about </i>
<i>something...!</i>

93
00:07:46,448 --> 00:07:47,981
What?

94
00:07:49,684 --> 00:07:52,953
{\an7}<i>But, how can Yota be</i>
<i>with you guys, too!?</i>

95
00:07:53,888 --> 00:07:55,456
{\an8}<i>Three Yotas...?</i>

96
00:07:58,792 --> 00:08:00,527
What is going
on here!?

97
00:08:07,668 --> 00:08:12,438
<i>[♪Whistling]</i>

98
00:08:14,006 --> 00:08:15,942
Whistling...?

99
00:08:15,974 --> 00:08:20,646
<i>[♪Whistling]</i>

100
00:08:30,822 --> 00:08:34,058
So, who are you?

101
00:08:34,726 --> 00:08:36,994
{\an1}[♪Whistling]

102
00:08:37,027 --> 00:08:38,662
What's this?

103
00:08:38,696 --> 00:08:42,900
{\an1}[♪Whistling]

104
00:08:42,933 --> 00:08:44,735
Huh?

105
00:08:44,768 --> 00:08:46,804
[gasp]

106
00:08:46,837 --> 00:08:49,640
Hold on...

107
00:08:49,673 --> 00:08:52,442
Yeah, you're...
Yota!

108
00:08:52,475 --> 00:08:54,744
[giggle]

109
00:08:54,777 --> 00:08:57,480
{\an1}[♪Louder Whistling]

110
00:08:58,548 --> 00:09:00,617
{\an1}[grunt]... Yota..!

111
00:09:01,551 --> 00:09:02,585
{\an1}Naruto.

112
00:09:03,452 --> 00:09:10,626
{\an1}[♪Whistling]

113
00:09:13,060 --> 00:09:14,663
Yota...

114
00:09:21,035 --> 00:09:22,603
Huh?

115
00:09:25,940 --> 00:09:27,542
[groaning]

116
00:09:28,543 --> 00:09:29,877
What's up?

117
00:09:29,911 --> 00:09:32,680
What did you do with
Yota!? Did you take
him somewhere, you-!?

118
00:09:32,713 --> 00:09:36,182
{\an4}Ino, putting him
through an
interrogation
won't work.

119
00:09:36,216 --> 00:09:38,485
{\an1}Naruto, you know
though, don't you?

120
00:09:39,152 --> 00:09:40,720
Know what?

121
00:09:40,754 --> 00:09:42,187
[groan]

122
00:09:42,221 --> 00:09:46,660
You saw something,
right? I mean...
maybe not...?

123
00:09:46,693 --> 00:09:49,595
If I didn't see
anything, how could
I have seen something?

124
00:09:49,628 --> 00:09:52,531
You know, you're a
lot shrewder than
you look.

125
00:09:52,565 --> 00:09:53,899
{\an1}Mmmhm!

126
00:09:53,933 --> 00:09:57,168
{\an5}Are you kidding!?
Why would that
impress you guys
so much?

127
00:09:57,201 --> 00:09:59,103
Come on! Let's go!

128
00:09:59,137 --> 00:10:00,573
Hey! What--!?

129
00:10:07,645 --> 00:10:10,014
Now, what did you
do with Yota!?

130
00:10:10,048 --> 00:10:11,015
Uh... Yota?

131
00:10:12,215 --> 00:10:15,152
You met him in the
schoolyard the other
day, didn't you...!?

132
00:10:15,185 --> 00:10:18,822
The only other person
who knows about Yota
besides us is you!

133
00:10:20,024 --> 00:10:21,758
[gasp]

134
00:10:32,702 --> 00:10:34,971
{\an1}Come on! Don't deny
it! You met Yota,
didn't you!?

135
00:10:35,005 --> 00:10:37,206
{\an1}And then you blabbed
about it to everyone!

136
00:10:37,239 --> 00:10:39,609
I don't know
who Yota is.

137
00:10:39,642 --> 00:10:42,243
He was a kid who
got lost near the
Village...

138
00:10:42,277 --> 00:10:45,547
We all felt bad for
him so we started
taking care of him.

139
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:50,251
{\an1}But then, today, when we
came here, everything was
a mess and Yota was gone!

140
00:10:50,285 --> 00:10:53,922
{\an1}So, this kid is some
kind of an outsider then?

141
00:10:53,955 --> 00:10:55,222
{\an3}[gasp]

142
00:10:55,255 --> 00:10:58,727
{\an1}Why would you guys
protect an outsider...

143
00:10:58,760 --> 00:11:01,096
{\an1}...but still look
at me that way!?

144
00:11:01,128 --> 00:11:02,763
[grunt]

145
00:11:02,796 --> 00:11:05,599
{\an1}What kind of thing
is that to say!?

146
00:11:07,768 --> 00:11:09,268
{\an1}He's so stuck up!

147
00:11:09,302 --> 00:11:10,804
[groan]

148
00:11:10,838 --> 00:11:14,707
{\an5}Well, maybe we did
question him kinda
hard without having
any proof...

149
00:11:15,141 --> 00:11:16,275
Huh?

150
00:11:16,309 --> 00:11:19,812
Maybe he really
doesn't know anything
about Yota.

151
00:11:19,846 --> 00:11:21,881
{\an1}[guilty sigh]

152
00:11:27,987 --> 00:11:31,757
{\an1}This really stinks!
Why's it always
have to be me!?

153
00:11:36,962 --> 00:11:39,263
{\an1}Ugh, now I'm lost.

154
00:11:41,599 --> 00:11:47,705
<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>[crying]</i>

155
00:11:47,738 --> 00:11:50,608
[gasp] Huh?

156
00:11:50,641 --> 00:11:55,880
[crying]

157
00:11:55,913 --> 00:11:58,848
Are you...?

158
00:12:02,218 --> 00:12:14,863
[crying]

159
00:12:14,897 --> 00:12:17,198
{\an1}Hey, could it be...?

160
00:12:17,232 --> 00:12:21,704
[crying]

161
00:12:21,737 --> 00:12:24,173
{\an1}Hey! Whoa! Just calm
it down, would ya!?

162
00:12:24,205 --> 00:12:26,008
What is it!?
What's the matter!?

163
00:12:26,041 --> 00:12:30,645
[crying]

164
00:12:30,678 --> 00:12:32,180
Who are you
anyway?

165
00:12:32,245 --> 00:12:34,649
I'm scared!
I'm so scared!

166
00:12:34,682 --> 00:12:36,651
Okay... but
what's your name?

167
00:12:36,684 --> 00:12:38,285
I'm... Yota!

168
00:12:38,719 --> 00:12:41,655
{\an1}Huh!? So you're the
one they were talking
about!

169
00:12:41,688 --> 00:12:42,589
<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>[crying harder]</i>

170
00:12:42,622 --> 00:12:46,225
ARGHHH!

171
00:12:49,129 --> 00:12:50,563
{\an1}Huh?

172
00:12:51,198 --> 00:12:53,733
{\an1}Weird, a sun shower?

173
00:12:53,766 --> 00:12:56,302
{\an1}Yota, is this...
your jutsu?

174
00:12:57,636 --> 00:12:59,338
{\an1}Wow, that's cool!

175
00:12:59,371 --> 00:13:03,142
{\an1}Man, I can't even do
stuff like Clone or
Transformation Jutsu.

176
00:13:03,175 --> 00:13:07,046
{\an1}And Iruka Sensei is
always getting on my
case about it, too.

177
00:13:08,981 --> 00:13:13,017
{\an1}You're an outsider
like me, but everybody
likes you...

178
00:13:13,918 --> 00:13:15,920
What a joke...
that's so unfair,
you know?

179
00:13:15,954 --> 00:13:17,387
{\an1}Boo!
Ahh!

180
00:13:17,421 --> 00:13:22,359
{\an1}Wait! I know you!
You are...
[blowing air]

181
00:13:22,392 --> 00:13:28,665
{\an4}Right? You were sitting
up on the iron rod the
other day and doing that
whatchamacallit-- Whistling!

182
00:13:28,699 --> 00:13:28,999
Oh!

183
00:13:35,705 --> 00:13:42,979
[♪Whistling]

184
00:13:43,780 --> 00:13:49,684
{\an1}Whoa...! [♪Whistling]

185
00:13:51,853 --> 00:13:57,759
[♪Whistling]

186
00:13:57,793 --> 00:14:00,327
{\an1}Can you teach me
how to whistle, too!?

187
00:14:00,361 --> 00:14:01,863
Huh?

188
00:14:01,897 --> 00:14:05,233
{\an1}When you started whistling
like that, it was like you
weren't all alone anymore!

189
00:14:05,267 --> 00:14:06,700
{\an1}It cheered you up!

190
00:14:06,734 --> 00:14:09,036
{\an1}I was just pretending!

191
00:14:09,069 --> 00:14:12,338
I only started
whistling to
distract myself...

192
00:14:12,372 --> 00:14:14,975
{\an1}Then that's what
Yota's gonna do, too!

193
00:14:15,009 --> 00:14:16,710
Look, you're already
friends with everyone-

194
00:14:19,013 --> 00:14:22,116
Uh... Huh!?

195
00:14:27,487 --> 00:14:29,388
Are you...?

196
00:14:31,991 --> 00:14:34,994
{\an1}[gasp] Hold still!

197
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,663
[hissing]

198
00:14:38,931 --> 00:14:39,932
{\an3}[gasp]

199
00:14:44,136 --> 00:14:49,208
{\an1}Will you teach me how
to whistle like you,
now? Pretty please?

200
00:14:49,241 --> 00:14:50,741
Sure!

201
00:14:57,447 --> 00:15:01,785
{\an1}All right, watch me.
First blow out without
pursing your lips, ya know?

202
00:15:01,818 --> 00:15:03,787
Then, you slowly
narrow them...

203
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:06,723
...and make wind
sounds like "wooosh!"

204
00:15:06,957 --> 00:15:08,758
Hm!

205
00:15:08,792 --> 00:15:18,801
[♪]

206
00:15:18,834 --> 00:15:28,878
[♪]

207
00:15:28,878 --> 00:15:38,820
[♪]

208
00:15:38,853 --> 00:15:48,896
[♪]

209
00:15:48,896 --> 00:15:58,838
[♪]

210
00:15:58,871 --> 00:16:08,915
[♪]

211
00:16:08,915 --> 00:16:14,486
[♪]

212
00:16:14,519 --> 00:16:16,121
{\an8}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>He's happy now...</i>

213
00:16:17,956 --> 00:16:20,292
{\an8}<i>So his happiness</i>
<i>turns into wind!</i>

214
00:16:24,996 --> 00:16:28,832
Listen!
[whistling melody]

215
00:16:29,334 --> 00:16:30,801
{\an1}What's that?

216
00:16:30,834 --> 00:16:33,504
{\an1}<i>[whistling melody echo]</i>

217
00:16:33,537 --> 00:16:36,106
<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>You. Are. My. Friend.</i>

218
00:16:37,074 --> 00:16:37,241
Huh?

219
00:16:39,343 --> 00:16:41,245
You are my
friend! Ya know?

220
00:16:42,179 --> 00:16:43,213
Hm?

221
00:16:43,247 --> 00:16:46,582
[laughing]

222
00:16:46,616 --> 00:16:48,518
{\an1}<i>(Akamaru)</i>
<i>[Barking]</i>

223
00:16:48,551 --> 00:16:49,352
{\an3}Hm.

224
00:16:49,385 --> 00:16:55,824
{\an1}<i>(Akamaru)</i>
<i>[Barking]</i>

225
00:16:55,857 --> 00:16:58,593
{\an1}Hey! There he is!
Come back, you!

226
00:16:58,627 --> 00:17:01,229
[barking]

227
00:17:01,263 --> 00:17:04,498
{\an1}Hey! Wait!

228
00:17:04,532 --> 00:17:06,467
No! No! Noooo!

229
00:17:09,470 --> 00:17:11,306
Ahhh!

230
00:17:12,073 --> 00:17:13,308
{\an1}That kid!? Again!?

231
00:17:13,342 --> 00:17:14,409
Yota!

232
00:17:15,242 --> 00:17:16,410
Ow!

233
00:17:16,445 --> 00:17:18,312
No doggies! No
doggies...! No!

234
00:17:18,346 --> 00:17:20,348
{\an1}Ahh! Whoa!

235
00:17:20,381 --> 00:17:22,383
{\an1}What did you guys
do to Yota!?

236
00:17:22,416 --> 00:17:24,251
{\an1}I have no idea!

237
00:17:24,285 --> 00:17:26,853
{\an1}I was just taking
Akamaru out for a
walk... ARGH!

238
00:17:26,886 --> 00:17:27,921
{\an1}And I saw that guy!

239
00:17:27,954 --> 00:17:29,222
{\an1}<i>[lightning zap]</i>

240
00:17:29,255 --> 00:17:31,624
{\an4}<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>Then thunder and</i>
<i>lightening started</i>
<i>goin' off everywhere!</i>

241
00:17:31,658 --> 00:17:33,960
{\an1}He's the one doing
this, isn't he!?

242
00:17:33,994 --> 00:17:35,195
{\an1}Argh!

243
00:17:37,464 --> 00:17:37,863
Yota?

244
00:17:37,896 --> 00:17:38,998
{\an1}Yeah! It's him!

245
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:42,335
{\an1}Yota...!

246
00:17:42,369 --> 00:17:43,936
Peh-peh-peh-peh!

247
00:17:44,570 --> 00:17:46,972
{\an1}So when Yota gets
angry, he makes
thunder and lightening?

248
00:17:48,974 --> 00:17:52,610
[screams]

249
00:17:55,079 --> 00:17:58,082
[giddy chuckles]

250
00:18:05,655 --> 00:18:06,457
[grunt]

251
00:18:08,592 --> 00:18:11,028
[laughing]

252
00:18:12,062 --> 00:18:13,864
Here, puppy!

253
00:18:26,175 --> 00:18:31,947
{\an1}One... two... three...

254
00:18:31,981 --> 00:18:36,519
{\an1}Four... five... six...

255
00:18:36,551 --> 00:18:42,023
{\an1}Seven... eight... nine...

256
00:18:42,057 --> 00:18:47,162
{\an1}Ten... eleven... twelve...

257
00:18:47,195 --> 00:18:49,531
Thirteen...

258
00:18:49,563 --> 00:18:50,764
I'll hide with
you, Naruto!

259
00:18:50,798 --> 00:18:54,134
You can't Yota!
They're gonna find
us both right away!

260
00:18:54,168 --> 00:18:56,203
[giggling]

261
00:18:56,236 --> 00:18:59,306
No, come on! You've
gotta stop acting
all happy like this!

262
00:18:59,339 --> 00:19:02,675
Otherwise the weather
will change, and then
they'll find us!

263
00:19:02,708 --> 00:19:06,513
{\an1}Now you're angry
with me, Naruto?

264
00:19:06,547 --> 00:19:10,450
Oh no! Not
crying! Just get
out of here! Shoo!

265
00:19:10,483 --> 00:19:13,386
{\an4}<i>(Kiba)</i>
<i>Ninety-eight,</i>
<i>ninety-nine....</i>
<i>one hundred!</i>

266
00:19:18,491 --> 00:19:20,226
{\an1}Ha! Found you, Naruto!

267
00:19:20,692 --> 00:19:22,562
Ugh! That Yota
got me caught!

268
00:19:26,064 --> 00:19:29,334
{\an1}Isn't anyone gonna
come and kick the
can to save me...?

269
00:19:29,367 --> 00:19:30,535
{\an1}Come on... anyone?

270
00:19:38,476 --> 00:19:39,677
[grunt]

271
00:19:44,315 --> 00:19:46,317
{\an1}Shikamaru, Choji, Ino,
Akamaru, Sakura...

272
00:19:49,587 --> 00:19:52,689
{\an1}That means Yota's
the only one left.

273
00:19:53,723 --> 00:19:55,325
Yota?

274
00:20:01,630 --> 00:20:03,600
{\an1}Yota...?

275
00:20:09,204 --> 00:20:11,173
{\an1}That means
Yota's crying!

276
00:20:12,074 --> 00:20:13,275
{\an1}Yota...!

277
00:20:20,715 --> 00:20:21,349
{\an1}[gasp]

278
00:20:24,252 --> 00:20:25,453
{\an1}No! Yota!

279
00:20:28,589 --> 00:20:30,056
{\an1}[grunt]

280
00:20:31,858 --> 00:20:36,163
{\an4}We're taking him into
custody. He'll be  kept
under strict observation
and interrogated.

281
00:20:36,196 --> 00:20:38,532
But Yota isn't a
danger to the Village!

282
00:20:38,565 --> 00:20:39,900
{\an1}We'll determine that.

283
00:20:39,933 --> 00:20:43,603
{\an1}Besides, all outsiders
are forbidden inside the
Village boarders.

284
00:20:43,637 --> 00:20:46,038
{\an1}You'll be summoned
later to give evidence.

285
00:20:46,071 --> 00:20:48,608
{\an1}Until then, return
home and stay there.

286
00:20:49,275 --> 00:20:51,076
{\an1}No way! 'Cause
Yota is my--!

287
00:20:57,749 --> 00:21:01,052
{\an1}[running breaths]

288
00:21:02,153 --> 00:21:06,758
{\an5}<i>(Thinking)</i>
<i>That was it. That</i>
<i>moment marked the end</i>
<i>of our days with Yota.</i>

289
00:21:11,596 --> 00:21:14,299
<i>And then...</i>

290
00:21:14,332 --> 00:21:16,700
{\an1}<i>We all let Yota die...</i>

291
00:22:56,459 --> 00:22:59,863
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Yota! Get a grip!</i>
<i>It's all okay!</i>

292
00:22:59,896 --> 00:23:03,767
<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>You guys... time</i>
<i>to go...</i>

293
00:23:03,799 --> 00:23:06,736
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>What are you talking about?</i>
<i>From now on we're gonna be--</i>

294
00:23:06,770 --> 00:23:10,707
{\an5}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>No matter what happens,</i>
<i>I will never forget</i>
<i>about you guys...  </i>

295
00:23:10,740 --> 00:23:14,677
{\an5}<i>(Yota)</i>
<i>But every last one</i>
<i>of you will forget</i>
<i>about me...</i>

296
00:23:14,710 --> 00:23:19,214
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>Next time on Naruto Shippuden:</i>
<i>"Lingering Snow"</i>

297
00:23:19,248 --> 00:23:21,383
<i>(Naruto)</i>
<i>How could we</i>
<i>forget you!?</i>

